bilingual.source: The dependent variable is affected by the independent variable.
bilingual.target: 因变量受自变量的影响。

bilingual.source: The range of this variable is very wide.
bilingual.target: 这个变量的值域非常广。

bilingual.source: The variable is undefined in the script.
bilingual.target: 变量在脚本中是未定义的。

bilingual.source: A Boole variable can only be true or false.
bilingual.target: 布尔变量只能取真或假。

bilingual.source: The variable in the experiment was the temperature.
The mathematical sym represents an unknown variable.
bilingual.target: 数学符号表示未知变量。

bilingual.source: This random variable can take different values.
bilingual.target: 这个随机变量可以取不同的值。

bilingual.source: You need to find the coefficient of each variable.
bilingual.target: 你需要找到每个变量的系数。

bilingual.source: The ptr points to the memory address of the variable.
bilingual.target: 指针指向变量的内存地址。

list.abstract: variable（英[ˈveəriəbl]，美[ˈveriəbl]），英语单词，作形容词用，为易变的；多变的；反复无定的。作名词用，为可变性；可变因素；变量。短语搭配有dependent variable（因变量），例句为“Awards can be for highly variable amounts.（奖金数量可以很不一样。）” variable形容词类近义词有mobile、liquid、unstable，相关反义词有invariable。

yingyinNormal.en: What would a theoretical physicist understand about an experiment anyway? I mean, you wouldn't know a confounding variable if two of them hit you in the face at the same time!
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个理论物理学家懂个屁的实验啊？！就算混杂和变量同时扇你耳光你都不会感觉到混杂变量！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we could if it were true. But as you live in the same building, you see each other all the time. The variable which has changed is the coitus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那得真的不见才行，可你们住在同一栋楼里，低头不见抬头见，唯一改变的变量是交媾。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you sure? 'Cause you only have one night with me, tiger, and I'm as flexible as a government-insured, zero-down, variable-rate mortgage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你确定吗？因为你跟我只有一晚上的时间，猛虎，而我就和政府担保的零首付浮息按揭一样灵活。

yingyinNormal.en: There was extensive damage to both the guide vanes and fan blades of the engine. Five compressor blades were fractured and eight variable guide vanes missing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 发动机上的导流叶片和风扇叶片都受到了大面积损伤，5个压缩机叶片断裂，还有8个可变导流叶片丢失。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Students' attitudes on the topic are <highlight>variable</highlight> and unstable, behavior is easily measurable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学生对这个话题的态度是多变和不稳定的，行为是很容易衡量的。

examination_example.sentence: Psychologist Nina Strohminger says she wants the effect to be real but cannot rule out some unknown confounding <highlight>variable</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 心理学家Nina Strohminger说她希望结果是真实的，但不能排除一些未知的混淆变量。

examination_example.sentence: There is plenty of evidence that the quality of the teachers is the most important <highlight>variable</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有大量事实表明教师的素质是最重要的可变因素。
